OL,3,CWhy are there grants for electric cars
OL,4,Cbut not solar panels in Jersey?
OL,6,FHowever, Jersey's Environment Minister
OL,7,Fsays his department is focusing
OL,8,Felsewhere to help the island become
OL,9,Fmore sustainable.
OL,11,FThe Bailiwick currently imports the
OL,12,Fbulk of its energy from France, the
OL,13,Fvast majority of which is clean power
OL,14,Fcoming from hydro and nuclear sources.
OL,16,FTherefore, the States is prioritising
OL,17,Fthe electrification of Jersey's
OL,18,Ftransport, and homes that still use
OL,19,Ffossil fuels.
