OL,3,CWhy are there grants for electric cars
OL,4,Cbut not solar panels in Jersey?
OL,6,FThose areas make up more than two
OL,7,Fthirds of emissions - reducing them is
OL,8,Fimperative if the island is to reach
OL,9,Fnet zero by 2050.
OL,11,FThat is why the government is helping
OL,12,Fpeople interested in switching to an
OL,13,Felectric car and low-carbon heating
OL,14,Fsystems.
OL,16,FCurrently, drivers in Jersey can get
OL,17,Fup to and, depending on their income,
OL,18,F, such as electric storage heaters and
OL,19,Fair source heat pumps.
