OL,3,CWhy are there grants for electric cars
OL,4,Cbut not solar panels in Jersey?
OL,6,FNevertheless, solar will still play a
OL,7,Fkey role as the island tries to become
OL,8,Fmore sustainable.
OL,10,FJersey Electricity is aiming for 5% of
OL,11,Fpower to be produced by ground-mounted
OL,12,Fpanels within a few years.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, for those that install
OL,15,Ftheir own panels, they should last for
OL,16,F25 years and lead to savings in the
OL,17,Flong-run.
