OL,3,CWhy are there grants for electric cars
OL,4,Cbut not solar panels in Jersey?
OL,6,FAccording to SunWorks, a Jersey solar
OL,7,Finstallation company, it would cost
OL,8,Faround #6,000 for a three-bedroom
OL,9,Fhouse to install 6 panels.
OL,11,FThat would generate savings of around
OL,12,F#600 a year - this means after
OL,13,Fapproximately 10 years, islanders
OL,14,Fwould make their money back, and then
OL,15,Fcontinue to have cheaper bills going
OL,16,Fforward.
